    "id": "cloche-cyn",
    "title": "Host workflow scripts must execute from main branch",
    "description": "When running the host workflow, executed scripts must come from main, even if operating in a worktree off a different branch. This ensures host-workflow fixes made on main are available to in-flight runs, even if they branched before the client-side workflow began.",
